title: Hong Kong GDP From Agriculture, Fishing, Mining and Quarrying
description: GDP from Agriculture in Hong Kong increased to 639 HKD Million in the second quarter of 2022 from 609 HKD Million in the first quarter of 2022. GDP from Agriculture in Hong Kong averaged 586.53 HKD Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 832 HKD Million in the first quarter of 2000 and a record low of 413 HKD Million in the first quarter of 2018. This page provides - Hong Kong Gdp From Agriculture- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Census and Statistics Department, Hong Kong
